2026-06-04 08:57:14,118  INFO    [169/295] ADDED — 31.8 Acres+/- Parsons Road Beaverdam District Hanover County, Virginia Tax Map Parcel Nos. 7815-63-2552, 7815-64-9318 & 7815-64-6825 Default having been made in the terms of a certain Deed of Trust dated May 3, 2022, and of record in the Clerk's Office, Circuit Court, Hanover County, Virginia, on May 4, 2022, in Deed Book 3352, Page 2027, W. Richard Hairfield, the undersigned Trustee having been requested to do so by the holder of the Note secured, will proceed to sell at public auction, for cash, on Thursday, May 21, 2026 at 11:00 a.m. in front of the Hanover County Courthouse, Hanover County, Virginia, the above-described property. At the sale, a $5,000.00 bidder's deposit may be required at the sole discretion of the Trustee and a purchaser's deposit of ten percent (10%) of the gross sales price of the property shall be required in cash, cashier's check or certified check, at the time of sale, with settlement to be made within ten (10) days thereafter. The property is being sold AS IS. The parcels may be sold separately or in bulk, at the discretion of the Trustee. Additional terms will be announced at the sale. Sale subject to post sale seller confirmation. For information contact: FORREST A. SANFORD, TRUSTEE Relationship Manager Colonial Farm Credit, ACA 7104 Mechanicsville Turnpike Mechanicsville | county: Hanover | sale: 2026-05-21
